    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for a Model Risk Category 3 assessment. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted given that the validation scope is explicitly bounded to the ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration and the regulatory claim is limited to that loading mode. Overall credibility is judged sufficient to support the intended 510(k) comparative performance submission.",
